<br>
My husband took over, deleted my baby warrior (He gave the excuse of doing my stats wrong) then created his own warrior. So now we've got his warrior to play.  He robbed me while I was at work (he emptied Sal's bank account) and picked up some pretty good weapons, IMO.<br>
<br>
<br>
For primary hand he got a Venemous Axe of something or other... The stats aren't all that great, but its got an 85 damage proc thats a lot of fun to play with, and makes soloing reds (at least at low levels) Possible.<br>
<br>
For offhand he picked up one of those Centi LS's that were mentioned earlier. <br>
<br>
I asked him what he did with the lammies, and he said that he sold one for 4k, kept the other in the bank for later use.  Anyway, we're sharing his warrior now, although I'm still putting in 90% of my game time in DAoC and he's putting in about the same amount into EQ, so you guys will most likely see him playing.  <br>
<br>
I must say its nice to play the low levels again, without a giant commitment to others. <p><p><font size=1><b>Fortuna Veldingard of Nimue, DAoC<br>
